author: Slidebean
description:
New spam filters, stricter voice cloning rules, and clear AI labels aim to stop fake tracks and protect artists.
On a $15.67 billion platform where musicians earn fractions of pennies per stream, is this enough to make a difference — or just the first step?

Get the full story on The Slidebean Stand-Up—streaming now on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, and other major podcast platforms. 

#Spotify #AImusic #MusicNews
title: Spotify finally cracking down on AI-generated music.
